rtunities these products are usually structured along defined themes and are normally denominated in us dollar euro and british pound most structured notes have standard parameters of principal protection while return potential is linked either to the performance of an underlying index such as dow jones nasdaq or libor or a basket of stocks hence when you invest in a structured note you may get a principal protection and b returns linked to the performance of an underlying market parameter  fixed income securities bonds fixed income securities are ideal for investors who want a regular income through coupon payment as well as for investors looking for an opportunity for capital appreciation through the sale of securities before maturity if the price moves up you can choose from a vast selection of fixed income securities with a variety of credit quality characteristics maturities and yields to meet your individual objectives click here for participation of retail customersinvestor in government securities issuances  mutual funds as a citibank customer you can choose from a variety of mutual funds and alternate investment options these funds are selected to suit a variety of investment objectives and risk profiles you can select funds across diverse asset classes including us equities emerging market equities global equities global bonds high yield bonds money market funds shariah compliant islamic equities real estate equities middle east equities and many more you have a wide range of mutual funds from some of the most reputed investment houses  islamic investment options if you are seeking shariah compliant investments please stop by your nearest citibank branch to speak with a registered wealth management consultant if you wish to invest please contact your nearest branch and get in touch with your relationship manager disclaimer investment products  this website does not constitute any offer or solicitation to buy or sell any investment product investors should 